{"tid":1961773,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"中環卑利街舖4年勁蝕逾千萬   業主劈價幅度達50%","createTime":"2020-04-07T04:22:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T13:51:41.000Z","uid":79563,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"80c79d0c013f0f576954bbd90af4ce5899906b11","tid":1961773,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T04:22:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/4fTWX02X.Vaf8CdFDaYbRA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDAw/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-04/e0ea6210-785d-11ea-b6df-527463447171\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F4fTWX02X.Vaf8CdFDaYbRA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjAwO2g9NDAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-04%2Fe0ea6210-785d-11ea-b6df-527463447171&h=3ce2e036&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n零售市道慘淡，舖位身價大跌，於高位接貨的投資者更要損手離場。中環卑利街一個地舖，原業主於2015年11月以2400萬元承接，剛以1500萬元沽出，持貨逾4年賬面虧損900萬元（37.5%），計及印花稅及代理佣金等開支，料勁蝕超過1140萬元。<br />\n<br />\n消息指出，中環卑利街18A至18B號福志樓地下4號舖，建築面積420方呎，去年起一直以3000萬元叫價放售，惟今年初受新冠肺炎疫情影響，2月已把意向價調低至2400萬元，最終更僅以1500萬元沽出，劈價幅度達50%，呎價約3.57萬元。舖位現由粉麵廠承租，月租3萬元，回報約2.4厘。<br />\n<br />\n代理指出，原業主當日買入該舖位是看好有關地段具收購潛力，但近年一直未見有任何收購活動，加上市況逆轉，決心蝕讓離場。"},{"pid":"f3d7bd8f88756d281e5649d66a0ccc0ddaf38ffb","tid":1961773,"uid":158755,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T05:05:18.000Z","msg":"為左收購潛力先買<br />\n守得5年就放都幾戇居"},{"pid":"bf2b5feb50f926479049948e510f9939435702cd","tid":1961773,"uid":33730,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T05:10:32.000Z","msg":"2015要2400萬420呎, 5萬幾一呎買貝沙灣都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9cfdfe140308a961dfeca528b697a95623b646d","tid":1961773,"uid":1633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f3d7bd8f88756d281e5649d66a0ccc0ddaf38ffb","tid":1961773,"uid":158755,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTi